  "detailed_description": "<h1>RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/c650aa492f5caaef331c00c31173a593.poster.avif?t=1771944772\" width=616 height=455 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/c650aa492f5caaef331c00c31173a593.webm?t=1771944772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Meow meow meow dear friends! There are <strong>Hidden Cats in London</strong>, let's find them all.<br>A short and pleasant experience in a big and pleasant illustration! Start with a Beautiful monochromatic scenario, relax, and find all the cats one by one to reveal the <strong>final colored art</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/0a6ad20028acdc4f763adf3613a77993.webp?t=1771944772\" width=21 height=20 /></span><strong>More than 560 Hidden Objects to find!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/0a6ad20028acdc4f763adf3613a77993.webp?t=1771944772\" width=21 height=20 /></span><strong>Play through different modes, find special cats, and unlock bonus levels!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/901af96cfcfcfa81f94ac2a66bef8a63.avif?t=1771944772\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LONDON - NORMAL MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 100 cats in fixed positions.<br></li><li>3 hints.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LONDON - ADVANCED MODE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 150 cats in random positions.<br></li><li>Find special cats and city people to earn hints and unlock bonus levels.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/0ee8187718a236defd313b170914b2f4.poster.avif?t=1771944772\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099080/extras/0ee8187718a236defd313b170914b2f4.webm?t=1771944772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIDDEN KITTENS BONUS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find 50 hidden kittens on each level: Book Shop, Pub, Tube Station, Music Studio, Palace Room, Christmas.<br></li><li>1 hint use.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACCESSIBILITY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark Mode<br></li><li>Invert Mouse Zoom<br></li><li>Mouse Drag Sensibility<br></li><li>Edge Screen Scrolling</li></ul>",
